{"tid":2487019,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國官方史上首次在台買房　擲台幣11.6億買豪宅　當員工宿舍","createTime":"2021-04-13T09:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T08:24:45.000Z","uid":35519,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ea601db1572b107590871b3e9c3eac49d0e0d6d2","tid":2487019,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">美利堅合眾國在台買房<br />\n買11.6億元豪宅當員工宿舍</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/B-6CoJSDIKwKlDzHwT7RGmAL-Eo=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HKTLBALYBBFTZPGWQUKUVSWKEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB-6CoJSDIKwKlDzHwT7RGmAL-Eo%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHKTLBALYBBFTZPGWQUKUVSWKEY.jpg&h=6e4201ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國在台協會（AIT）2018年砸11.6億台幣，買下台北市天母使館特區的「新美齊天母」整棟預售豪宅，將作為員工宿舍，最新實價登錄與地籍資料揭露，該案今年3月25日完成買賣登記，而買方為「美利堅合眾國」，證實美國官方首次在台購置不動產。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/61kl7dN5hNUqpiYO1paiK8z6Avw=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2UKCODPREVDSJFD5ADJU3RT3SA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F61kl7dN5hNUqpiYO1paiK8z6Avw%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2UKCODPREVDSJFD5ADJU3RT3SA.jpg&h=a8a00c8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新實登揭露，「新美齊天母」基地302.5坪，位於台北市士林區中山北路六段441巷，全棟1~12樓共1643.03坪，格局包含45房22廳35衛，以及46個車位，2018年11月底以預售案11.6億成交，未拆算車位，單坪約70.6萬。而扣除1樓外，每層權狀64.56坪，內含6.74 坪陽台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/D4rFa9Twz0wKwSqthHpFoBwFqME=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JX6JKTVHTZELDNOJQZKKY4UJGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD4rFa9Twz0wKwSqthHpFoBwFqME%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJX6JKTVHTZELDNOJQZKKY4UJGA.jpg&h=bee9120f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謄本資訊顯示，買方為美利堅合眾國，地址登記在內湖區金湖路的AIT辦事處，今年3月25日完成買賣登記，該筆交易並未貸款。<br />\n<br />\n建商新美齊過去受訪時透露，AIT當初看過天母區域當年度所有建案，最終選擇「新美齊天母」的原因，為新美齊為上市建商，過去作品深獲口碑；因應AIT需求，原規劃雙拼格局，改為1層1戶，另獲美國國務院下屬OBO（海外建築業務局）高規格的審查標準，耐震表現可通過美規檢驗，全案預計今年第四季交屋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/JzOc7ZyFQTw2IrphrNrZL2MmcOo=/760x242/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FDYLOMIITRHOBDWWLCZN4H6MDI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJzOc7ZyFQTw2IrphrNrZL2MmcOo%3D%2F760x242%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFDYLOMIITRHOBDWWLCZN4H6MDI.jpg&h=3c892823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣房屋天母七段加盟店店長黃翊華分析，拆算車位單價約在90~100萬間，以天母新案單坪均價110萬來看，價格堪稱實惠，原因不脫是整棟交易；天母有美國學校、日僑學校等，公園綠地多，外國氣息濃厚，又有新光、高島屋、SOGO等3間百貨，生活機能便利，均為吸引AIT買下新大樓作為員工宿舍的原因。<br />\n<br />\n全球居不動產情報室總監陳炳辰表示，天母因有日僑、美國學校等進駐，外籍人士移居帶動房市，區域多有高單價餐飲消費，如今商圈雖逐步沒落，仍具一定生活機能，天母仍舊是外籍人士的指標居住區。這次買方購置房地作為員工宿舍，可見體恤外派員工，選擇天母，讓子女在教育、居住生活風格上，易與國外融合。至於單價低於百萬元，屬在地行情，推估未來轉手易漲難跌。（楊明峰／台北報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/gFm28cF90zcFiDu-8ItJprDQB-Y=/760x506/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/P5N7VIBB5NBYTJUPIQRXXUIFMM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgFm28cF90zcFiDu-8ItJprDQB-Y%3D%2F760x506%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FP5N7VIBB5NBYTJUPIQRXXUIFMM.jpg&h=c2ed5b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210413/4ZEM26HGWBACTENLV5A66GHXUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210413%2F4ZEM26HGWBACTENLV5A66GHXUY%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11KEelou7VeK%2FuoOlBiwx%2FXk%3D&h=3757abdc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210413%2F4ZEM26HGWBACTENLV5A66GHXUY%2F&h=f366d344\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210413/4ZEM26HGWBACTENLV5A66GHXUY/</a>"},{"pid":"1760ec3169303d648b4dff29f31f18acba8abf10","tid":2487019,"uid":279938,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"賣出香港宿舍，買入台北宿舍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ecb91c52935af07a7d0bb05054a6a239a0f4c9","tid":2487019,"uid":35519,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"美帝真鬼馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港一收到錢，就去台灣買樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">恒隆25.66億港元 <br />\n完成收購美國領事館壽臣山物業</span><br />\n<strong>2021-<ins>02-25</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/2/1614237574_Ak-1280w.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F2%2F1614237574_Ak-1280w.JPG&h=53b3e2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恒隆集團及恒隆地產公布，完成向美國駐港總領事館收購香港壽山村道37號物業。集團公告指，土地註冊處獲告知，美國已遵從外交義務，就物業出售獲得中國中央政府書面同意，所以已為該協議備忘錄進行註冊，投標人收購物業事項在今日完成。<br />\n<br />\n壽山村道37號物業由美國政府於1948年購入，並持有至今作美國駐港領事館宿舍之用，現為6幢低密度住宅物業提供26個單位及52個車位。<br />\n<br />\n恒隆去年以25.66億元，向美國駐港總領事館買入壽山村道37號物業，樓面地價約54,000元，但基於壽臣山地皮並非普通房地產，涉及中美兩國之間的外交事務，需符合外交義務的要求，要先得到中央政府同意。"},{"pid":"009ed616d21a4f3d48f56a2fe0b06c2006ea1f91","tid":2487019,"uid":34444,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />共產黨幾時武攻？又話唔會忍美帝？又下緊一盤很大的棋？"},{"pid":"2fc5b12a1